I will, I have had this since Monday, and my lady is the one pushing me to go.  I'm a man (maybe a stupid man) and the only reason I would go to the Doctor is if I'm kicking the bucket.  The only furneral I will go to is my own, and I'm not sure if I will even go to that one.lol  I'll be ok, and thanks for the concerns.
   
   I also have acid reflux and it makes me miserable some times.  I take a Zantac and it goes away.  Thats just fine with me.
   
  Rees

Laura Kimberley <ghuny1@...> wrote:
              Rees, 
  Geez guy, I hope your ok, I had one helluva chest pain attack last night myself, and thought omg, but it turns out is was a really bad case of indegestion, alot of gas! lol but it sure scared the puddin out of me. Take an asprin right away for sure. Don't play with chest pains!! Work will always be there!! You may not!!  
  So take care of yourself!!
  LK
